sources.description:
Sleuth joins forces with daring British agent in ruthless spy chase!
When enemy agents obtain leaked secrets about a guided missile reservation, the chief of America's counterspy division (Howard St. John) and Scotland Yard's best investigator Ron Randell get on an investigative trail which quickly leads to a reservation secretary.

Original title: Counterspy Meets Scotland Yard (1950)
This film is subtitled in many language options.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/0dRz6kHJk-4


Director: Seymour Friedman
Writers: Harold Greene, Phillips Lord
Stars: Howard St. John, Ron Randell, Amanda Blake
Genres: Colorized classics, Film-Noir, Crime, Drama
